Drop a real PNG (3840x2160 recommended) at packages/torrentos-theme/wallpaper.png.
The build script refuses to package without it. Suggested generator:

    convert -size 3840x2160 \
        gradient:'#0A1628-#1E6FFF' \
        -blur 0x80 \
        wallpaper.png

or use any flow-field renderer keyed to seed 'torrentos-riptide'.
